## Taking part in this research

### What we're doing

We're researching {{study.method}} to improve {{project.name}}. This research helps us understand user needs and make better decisions about the service.

### What will happen in this session

{{#meta.session_duration}}This session will take about {{meta.session_duration}} minutes.{{/meta.session_duration}} We will:

- Ask you some questions about your experience
- {{#meta.has_tasks}}Ask you to try some tasks using a prototype or the service{{/meta.has_tasks}}
- {{#meta.has_tasks}}Ask you to think aloud as you work{{/meta.has_tasks}}

You can take breaks at any time. If you feel uncomfortable, you can skip questions or stop the session.

### Recording and data use

{{#meta.recording_audio}}We would like to record audio during this session.{{/meta.recording_audio}}
{{#meta.recording_video}}We would like to record video during this session.{{/meta.recording_video}}
{{#meta.recording_screen}}We may capture screenshots or screen recordings.{{/meta.recording_screen}}

The recordings help us:
- Review what we learned
- Share findings with the team
- Improve the service

{{#meta.recording_audio}}You can ask us to stop recording at any time.{{/meta.recording_audio}}

We will:
- Store your data securely in approved systems
- Limit access to the research team{{#meta.team_name}} ({{meta.team_name}}){{/meta.team_name}}
- Delete recordings {{#meta.retention_period}}after {{meta.retention_period}}{{/meta.retention_period}}{{^meta.retention_period}}within 2 years{{/meta.retention_period}}
- Not share your name or contact details in reports or presentations
- Use pseudonyms (like "Participant 1") in any outputs

### Your choice to take part

Taking part in this research is voluntary. You can:
- Decide not to take part
- Stop at any time without giving a reason
- Skip any questions you don't want to answer
- Ask us to delete your data up to {{#meta.withdrawal_deadline}}{{meta.withdrawal_deadline}}{{/meta.withdrawal_deadline}}{{^meta.withdrawal_deadline}}2 weeks after the session{{/meta.withdrawal_deadline}}

This will not affect any government services you use.

### Data protection

We handle your personal data in line with UK GDPR and the Data Protection Act 2018.

The legal basis for processing your data is **public task** — improving government services.

{{#meta.dpia_completed}}A Data Protection Impact Assessment has been completed for this research.{{/meta.dpia_completed}}

Your rights:
- Ask what data we hold about you
- Ask us to correct inaccurate data
- Ask us to delete your data (within the withdrawal deadline)
- Object to how we use your data

